    "We compared FinAgent with 9 baseline methods in terms of 6 financial metrics.",
    "Table 7 and Figure 4 demonstrate our method significantly outperforms existing baselines, especially remarkable improvements in profitability, and setting a new benchmark in the field.",
    "We compare and evaluate the trading performance of FinAgent with four widely accepted conventional benchmark trading strategies (B&H, MACD, KDJ&RSI and ZMR) and five advanced algorithms.",
    "Among these, SAC [10], PPO [33] and DQN [20] are three models employed deep reinforcement learning (RL) methods, FinGPT [49] is based on LLM, and another is FinMem [55] that based on LLM Agents.",
